  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518600/extras/6e4d2248be0a53875408b1139e06d5e7.avif?t=1727954387\" width=400 height=225 /></span><br><br>Snake Jump is a third-person vertical platformer without checkpoints where you play as a snake. From down in the jungle you will go on an adventure, conquer obstacles  and complete a thrilling parcour. Try to climb various obstacles to see what heights you can reach as a snake. The goal? Simple. Reach the goal of the obstacle cours and a beautiful mystery awaits you! How far can you go? Find out and see.<br><br>Don't want to go on this journey alone? Don't worry! Play with up to five friends and take on this adventure together!<br><br>Snake Jump can be played on keyboard and mouse or any controller.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518600/extras/d8b445663be2fb98228fddeb9ec16596.poster.avif?t=1727954387\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518600/extras/d8b445663be2fb98228fddeb9ec16596.webm?t=1727954387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
